 (* Write a function to convert the given tuple to a key-value dictionary using adjacent elements. https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/-convert-tuple-to-adjacent-pair-dictionary/ *)
let adjacent_pairs_to_dict (x, y) =
  let x_key = x.key in
  let x_value = x.value in
  let y_key = y.key in
  let y_value = y.value in
  let x_key_value = (x_key, x_value) in
  let y_key_value = (y_key, y_value) in
  let x_key_value_dict = (x_key_value, x_value_dict) in
  let y_key_value_dict = (y_key_value, y_value_dict)

let adjacent_pairs_to_dict (x, y) =
  let x_key = x.key in
  let x_value = x.value in
  let y_key = y.key in
  let y_value = y.value in
  let x_key_value = (x_key, x_value) in
  let y_key_value = (y_key, y_value) in
  let x_key_value_dict = (x_key_value, x_value_dict) in
  let y_key_value_dict = (y_key_value, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key_value_dict, x_value_dict) in
  let y

 (* Write a function to convert the given tuple to a key-value dictionary using adjacent elements. https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/-convert-tuple-to-adjacent-pair-dictionary/ *)
let adjacent_pairs_to_dict (x, y) =
  let x_key = x.key in
  let x_value = x.value in
  let y_key = y.key in
  let y_value = y.value in
  let x_key_value = (x_key, x_value) in
  let y_key_value = (y_key, y_value) in
  let x_key_value_dict = (x_key_value, x_value_dict) in
  let y_key_value_dict = (y_key_value, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key_value_dict, x_value_dict) in
  let y_value_dict = (y_key_value_dict, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key_value_dict, x_value_dict) in
  let y_value_dict = (y_key_value_dict, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key_value_dict, x_value_dict) in
  let y_value_dict = (y_key_value_dict, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key_value_dict, x_value_dict) in
  let y_value_dict = (y_key_value_dict, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key_value_dict, x_value_dict) in
  let y_value_dict = (y_key_value_dict, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key_value_dict, x_value_dict) in
  let y_value_dict = (y_key_value_dict, y_value_dict) in

  let x_key = x.key in
  let x_value = x.value in
  let y_key = y.key in
  let y_value = y.value in
  let x_key_value = (x_key, x_value) in
  let y_key_value = (y_key, y_value) in
  let x_key_value_dict = (x_key_value, x_value_dict) in
  let y_key_value_dict = (y_key_value, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key_value_dict, x_value_dict) in
  let y_value_dict = (y_key_value_dict, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key_value_dict, x_value_dict) in
  let y_value_dict = (y_key_value_dict, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key_value_dict, x_value_dict) in
  let y_value_dict = (y_key_value_dict, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key_value_dict, x_value_dict) in
  let y_value_dict = (y_key_value_dict, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key_value_dict, x_value_dict) in
  let y_value_dict = (y_key_value_dict, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key_value_dict, x_value_dict) in
  let y_value_dict = (y_key_value_dict, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key_value_dict, x_value_dict) in
  let y_value_dict = (y_key_value_dict, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key_value_dict, x_value_dict) in
  let y_value_dict = (y_key_value_dict, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key

 (* Write a function to convert the given tuple to a key-value dictionary using adjacent elements. https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/-convert-tuple-to-adjacent-pair-dictionary/ *)
let adjacent_pairs_to_dict (x, y) =
  let x_key = x.key in
  let x_value = x.value in
  let y_key = y.key in
  let y_value = y.value in
  let x_key_value = (x_key, x_value) in
  let y_key_value = (y_key, y_value) in
  let x_key_value_dict = (x_key_value, x_value_dict) in
  let y_key_value_dict = (y_key_value, y_value_dict) in
  let x_value_dict = (x_key_value_dict, x_value_dict) in
  let y_value_dict = (y_key_value_dict, y_value_dict) in
